SriLankan Air to Operate Special Flight From Tokyo on March 17

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e   a n d   A s a n t h a   S i r i m a n n e
-- 
2011-03-16T09:11:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/srilankan-air-to-operate-special-flight-from-tokyo-on-march-17.html
SriLankan Airlines said it will
operate a special flight from  Tokyo  to  Colombo  on March 17 for
its citizens wishing to leave  Japan  after an earthquake and
tsunami in the far eastern nation.  SriLankan will continue its regular weekly flights as
scheduled from the Japanese capital, it said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
 anushao@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Hari Govind at 
 hgovind@bloomberg.net  